Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛往哪看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞到你是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那属于不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们先冷静地…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话真多 给别人添麻烦了就该有所表示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱吗 我没有多少钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就把相机拿来 还有手表
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相机可不行 这是我吃饭的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你高抬贵手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧 陶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样对待游客呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娜美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条街的名声会越来越臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭就臭呗 你少管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.26,0:01:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会要你的命的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多在你手脚上开几个洞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了袒护这陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要对我开枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要去跟莫利纳的老板娘告状
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想被那家店拒之门外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这才像话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之后最好做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指比赛吗 正合我意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把枪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是坏掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗 虽然很感谢你帮助了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救助费 5000美元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经很便宜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个叫陶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是出了名的凶狠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好 你已经死在他手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么好心帮你 你至少感激一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就好人做到底 别缠着我了好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么行 我也以身犯险了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就要5000美元？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这金额能在这里奢侈地生活一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会有那么多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给我这台相机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 这可是我吃饭的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你是做哪一行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碌碌无闻的摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影师？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也是来拍摄那个的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜者 鲜血女王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但魄力十足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些战后退役的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我们用来参加赌博摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经成为了这里的一大产业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个机器人…是叫AS来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的警察居然会认可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是军用武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小镇只认钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 看起来是挺繁荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是能给它来一篇全方位报道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮纳策奖一定非你莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 5000美元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那个叫普利策奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是世界上独一无二的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有各式各样的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野蛮人 丛林法兰绒 西北风还有飓风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂得真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 我可是出赛队伍的老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有最棒的AS和团队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在街角向我这种人要钱的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会拥有那种机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的有嘛 只是需要零件钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩两个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 壮观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个能叫…壮观？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱利 你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是重型机械的修理工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油压都是一回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然的确是破烂不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要买得起零件就能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 亚修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是需要两组50号肌肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有椎间盘减震
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资金有着落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位雷蒙老板会替我们出钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麻烦你尽快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行 我又没有同意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当借给我的 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是今晚的比赛能赢的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区5000美元 马上就能还你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这凭这破烂？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然机体不是最佳状态
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但驾驶员是一流的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫里克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人称「密林荒鹫」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾是美国海军的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止击毁敌机数量超过十架的老手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不信…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你见着他你就信了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 里克在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 刚才倒是见他喝得烂醉如泥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事了 娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克虽然品行不正
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还没到该死的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他是驾驶员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我要代替他驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你有经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能开得动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 娜美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说里克被捅死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治安真乱呀 怕怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过吧 让你做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就不爽那个美国佬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是不可一世的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是老天有眼 给他报应了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你们的对手就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是陶的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的机体也是上等货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去了 那家伙不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定也会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须要打赢比赛赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非赢不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 打扰到你了 雷蒙老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那5000美元我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.42,0:08:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你是自暴自弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太鲁莽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四面楚歌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里克在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找里克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的旧识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了 就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人从背后捅了一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 亏我还反复叮嘱他要注意背后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是他的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在三年前的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说里克成为了这里的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 我说了他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想报名参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为这个竞技场的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些对不住里克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过正好有这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能雇用我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会驾驶AS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,略懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,略懂？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是不缺你这种傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是军用的特殊设备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是常人无法驾驭的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂了吗 懂了就快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不准乱摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用这架机体参赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 只是会很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以里克的技术来说恐怕不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口气真大 你对这架机体懂多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这架机体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是RK-91的初期型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有采用燃气涡轮引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在功率和重量方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不如后来成为主流的92
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是以极限战斗机动为前提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在扭力控制上有些毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也在驾驶员技术能弥补的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这部机体的问题在于冷却系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗略看来 你们特意使用了原厂件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劝你们别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然都说市面的外贸空调兼容性不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但坚持十分钟不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还便宜许多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好省下这些钱买全新的肌肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说得好像你很懂的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我们宝贵的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然 你们保养得很用心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最早驾驶的型号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然还有能活动的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你就是一个空有理论的外行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是外行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是专家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 娜美 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆就请他来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 反正也是死马当活马医
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想参赛就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但钱怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有零件的话 它连站都站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱的话 我能支援3000美元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我信用卡的限额了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然有点兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种押冷门也挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是热门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里是为了找某样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不常见的驾驶服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方很强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且凶狠残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去去就来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说不定他真的挺有本事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么看出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的体格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有AS驾驶员的常见特征
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手肘手腕有厚厚的一层茧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知识方面也是专业的水准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好 他真的是个高手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经弄清它的脾气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一场 种类 徒手搏击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨妖 驾驶员 陶光闻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十字弩 驾驶员 相良宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那破烂还叫十字弩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀 酷不酷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好名字 不过比不上强弩兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强…弩？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种用来攻城的石弓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}杀 杀 杀 杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁 还有脸来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管是谁在驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要求饶已经来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜者 十字弩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发…发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陶晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体旋转得那么猛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连AS的冲击吸收系统也保护不了驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是遭遇了一场严重车祸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是普通的驾驶员根本办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换言之 那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高手 高手中的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是我们赢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道他能行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前不是还说他不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一桩 重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也能雇我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能保证住宿费和三餐就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 拜托你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松了一口气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 拍到好照片了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看比赛看得太入神 忘了拍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里加一扎啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:36.36,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.46,note2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(90,45)}两扎啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也真是随意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像已经把里克给忘了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总比沮丧要好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你是在哪儿学会驾驶AS的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赫尔马基斯坦内战时期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从敌军手中抢来的野蛮人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那已经是六七年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你参加过游击队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可看你和我年纪相差不大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 你还是个孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我不该问这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我也能向你提问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架野蛮人是从哪里弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是旧机体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不是私人能买到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在故乡村庄的郊外捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这个国家三年前还在打仗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们村被烧毁 我和家人也失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙儿都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那架野蛮人就是袭击村庄那伙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为燃料耗尽就被遗弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把它藏进山里 原本打算日后卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还有想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而却没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾试过在这里的一楼跳舞卖艺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可根本没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就参加了竞技场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么赚钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可赚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是升到A级后连胜的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想过得多奢侈都不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我对高级公寓之类的不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你赚钱来准备做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想重建村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用在这里赚到的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把荒芜的田地恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修桥修路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再重建学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 以前我就读的一间小小的校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然老师死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那确实是一所好学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么脸色阴沉沉的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我们这边喝个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他们彻底打成一片了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是必须的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我可是赞助商 是最牛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副施恩图报的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 来喝个痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天辛苦了 回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住的旅馆在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那我就不多送了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上10点机库前汇合 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上一个人走夜路是很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是承蒙「关照」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是特意来还礼的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输不起就想拿我出气是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人真是烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我话说前头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每骂我一句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就赏你一个耳光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你还没听懂规则啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:20:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 我接下来会好好教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你雇的那个臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把他给收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗介？你这个禽兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过不可以讲脏话的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫宗介吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜他现在已经在附近的胡同里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲着地面一命呜呼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是陶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的手下已经亲着地面进入梦乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开她 我不想惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我避开了气管 神经 颈动脉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要我稍微一动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我发誓以后再也不动她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发…发誓 是你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把陶放了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我还是应该杀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那类人不会轻易善罢甘休的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这可不一定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计他也应该怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们俩的住所都被他们查到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有接待外国人的高级酒店倒还好说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我和未成年人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼梦话！
